{"TopicId":180683,"ForumId":20,"TopicTitle":"Decrease Control Authority at high speeds.","CreatedByName":"TheKurgan","CreatedById":164104,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-12-19T01:07:53Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"TheKurgan","CreatedById":164104,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-12-19T01:07:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHello all,\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI have been creating some extremely fast jets, drones and modular missiles lately, and I was thinking that a mod that could decrease the control surface max deflection, or preferably their authority at high speeds would be awesome.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe jets and missiles I have created, some that do almost mach 5 (with ZERO custom parts) , have to have very low authority when doing speeds in excess of mach 1.5, or they explode from g forces when attempting maneuvers... because of this very low authority, they handle like \u00A0turds at low speeds. I know in reality you would just use less input, but the AI didn\u0027t get the memo...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDoes anyone have the expertise to create such a plugin?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMy modding skills are definitely not there yet.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis Modular Missile peaked at mach 4.98\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/k-michRrmbI?start=134\u0026amp;feature=oembed\u0022 width=\u0022480\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-12-19T01:19:03Z\u0022 title=\u002212/19/2018 01:19  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00225 yr\u0022\u003EDecember 19, 2018\u003C/time\u003E by TheKurgan\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Nightside","CreatedById":150244,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-12-19T01:35:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs Dynamic Deflection still around?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"TheKurgan","CreatedById":164104,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-12-19T01:39:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHmm... looking at it now. Last update was for 1.3. Going to peek at the source code.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"TheKurgan","CreatedById":164104,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-12-19T05:41:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/150244-nightside/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022150244\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/150244-nightside/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Nightside\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0Thanks for that tip!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI found a fork from the original repository that was updated for Authority vs deflection, I recompiled it for 1.5.1, and it works good enough for what I want it for.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCheers!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-12-19T05:41:19Z\u0022 title=\u002212/19/2018 05:41  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00225 yr\u0022\u003EDecember 19, 2018\u003C/time\u003E by TheKurgan\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Errol","CreatedById":118622,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-12-20T21:00:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223507272\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022180683\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221545198060\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022164104\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022TheKurgan\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 12/19/2018 at 12:41 AM, TheKurgan said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/150244-nightside/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022150244\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/150244-nightside/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Nightside\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0Thanks for that tip!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI found a fork from the original repository that was updated for Authority vs deflection, I recompiled it for 1.5.1, and it works good enough for what I want it for.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCheers!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMind sharing with the rest of the class?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"TheKurgan","CreatedById":164104,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-12-20T21:06:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHere is where I found it:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://github.com/blackliner/DynamicControls\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://github.com/blackliner/DynamicControls\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI don\u0027t see any licence in there at all...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWell... I\u0027m sure if I have done somthing wrong, a moderator will jump in \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:P\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E\u00A0so here it is:\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.dropbox.com/s/lrnk63i7y11magf/Dynamic%20Controls.zip?dl=0\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://www.dropbox.com/s/lrnk63i7y11magf/Dynamic Controls.zip?dl=0\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"wasml","CreatedById":120438,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-12-21T23:20:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf you\u0027re looking for a mod with a listed license Crzyrndm had a mod \u0022Dynamic Deflection\u0022 Here:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed9908954659\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/105289-13-the-plugin-workshop-small-plugins-of-varied-function/\u0026amp;\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:228px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat was originally GPLv3 but released as public domain here: \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/163707-no-longer-maintaining/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003Ehttps://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/163707-no-longer-maintaining/\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEdit: looks like DynamicControls was forked from Crzyrndm\u0027s work\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-12-21T23:21:52Z\u0022 title=\u002212/21/2018 11:21  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00225 yr\u0022\u003EDecember 21, 2018\u003C/time\u003E by wasml\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003EAdditional info\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"TheKurgan","CreatedById":164104,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-12-21T23:28:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/120438-wasml/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022120438\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/120438-wasml/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@wasml\u003C/a\u003E Yes, I checked out the original by Crzyrndm and I didn\u0027t see the licence, but later found it. like you said GPLv3. So it\u0027s ok to change it, and share it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-12-21T23:29:20Z\u0022 title=\u002212/21/2018 11:29  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00225 yr\u0022\u003EDecember 21, 2018\u003C/time\u003E by TheKurgan\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"wasml","CreatedById":120438,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-12-21T23:36:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/164104-thekurgan/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022164104\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/164104-thekurgan/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@TheKurgan\u003C/a\u003E Note the second link - When Crzyrndm left they changed the license to public domain - not sure how that impacts revives (allows more freedom to do as you please?)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}